OL,3,CHow thousands of hours of CCTV helped
OL,4,Cpolice catch a murderer
OL,6,FCCTV footage shows Marcin Majerkiewicz
OL,7,Fcarrying Stuart Everett's body parts
OL,8,Fin a bag for life as he walks towards
OL,9,Fthe woods to dispose of them, before
OL,10,Freturning with an empty bag.
OL,12,FWarning: Article contains some
OL,13,Fdistressing details
OL,15,FA murderer obsessed with horror films
OL,16,Fwho killed and dismembered his
OL,17,Fpensioner housemate was caught after
OL,18,Fpolice scoured thousands hours of CCTV
OL,19,Fto reveal him carrying his victim's
OL,20,Fbody parts across a city.
