OL,3,CHow thousands of hours of CCTV helped
OL,4,Cpolice catch a murderer
OL,6,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, who police say
OL,7,Fhad a "particular affinity for gore
OL,8,Fand torture", bludgeoned Stuart
OL,9,FEverett, 67, to death in their home
OL,10,Fbefore using a hack saw to cut him
OL,11,Finto "possibly hundreds" of pieces.
OL,13,FBut police only became aware of the
OL,14,Fcrime when a member of the public
OL,15,Fdiscovered Mr Everett's lower torso
OL,16,Fand thighs wrapped in cling film in an
OL,17,Fabandoned bunker in Kersal Dale nature
OL,18,Freserve, in Salford on 4 April 2024.
