OL,3,CHow thousands of hours of CCTV helped
OL,4,Cpolice catch a murderer
OL,6,FThe human remains were initially
OL,7,Funidentified, along with how they got
OL,8,Fthere, but as police combed through
OL,9,Fthousands of hours-worth of CCTV they
OL,10,Fnoticed a man going to the "deposition
OL,11,Fsite" with a heavy bag and returning
OL,12,Fwithout it.
OL,14,FDetective Sergeant Heidi Cullum, who
OL,15,Fworks in Greater Manchester Police's
OL,16,FVisual Evidence Retrieval and Analysis
OL,17,FUnit (VERA), dedicated to trawling
OL,18,Fthrough CCTV, says it was the
OL,19,Fbreakthrough the team needed.
