OL,3,CHow thousands of hours of CCTV helped
OL,4,Cpolice catch a murderer
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Heidi Cullum, whose
OL,7,Fteam trawled CCTV, describes the
OL,8,Fmoment they spotted their suspect
OL,10,F"We'd spent the initial days
OL,11,Fretrieving as much footage as we
OL,12,Fcould," she said.
OL,14,F"When we started to be able to view
OL,15,Fsome of these thousands of hours of
OL,16,Ffootage one of the team got the
OL,17,Fbreakthrough when they noticed this
OL,18,Findividual, who stood out in
OL,19,Fparticular because he was carrying a
OL,20,Fblue bag for life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
