OL,6,F"It was quite a large bag, but he was
OL,7,Freally struggling with the weight of
OL,8,Fit, which was obviously one of the
OL,9,Fcriteria we were looking for.
OL,11,F"We knew that the body parts of Stuart
OL,12,Fthat were found, although we didn't
OL,13,Fknow Stuart at the time, were
OL,14,Fsignificantly heavy so we knew it
OL,15,Fwould be not an easy, walking along
OL,16,Fwith a light carrier bag.
OL,18,F"So this individual stood out because
OL,19,Fof the size, the shape and everything
OL,20,Fabout the bag.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
