OL,3,CHow thousands of hours of CCTV helped
OL,4,Cpolice catch a murderer
OL,6,F"He was, he was moving it hand to
OL,7,Fhand, he was having to stop, rub his
OL,8,Fhands, and took quite a long time to
OL,9,Fwalk a relatively short space that we
OL,10,Fhad him on camera at the time."
OL,12,FAfter disappearing into the woods, the
OL,13,Fteam was then able to spot him, 10
OL,14,Fminutes later, carrying an empty bag
OL,15,Fbefore returning home the same way he
OL,16,Fcame.
