OL,3,CHow thousands of hours of CCTV helped
OL,4,Cpolice catch a murderer
OL,6,FOnce detectives had identified the
OL,7,Findividual they were in a "race
OL,8,Fagainst time" before footage was
OL,9,Fdeleted to track the man they believed
OL,10,Fto be their suspect.
OL,12,FThey were able to follow him onto a
OL,13,Fbus, and - through tracing his ticket
OL,14,F- discovered he had made a number of
OL,15,Fother journeys that day, including one
OL,16,Fto a site where he had potentially
OL,17,Fhidden more of his victim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
