OL,3,CHow thousands of hours of CCTV helped
OL,4,Cpolice catch a murderer
OL,6,FIt also meant police were able to
OL,7,Fnarrow down the location of his
OL,8,FMajerkiewicz's home, and while out
OL,9,Ftrawling for more CCTV, officers
OL,10,Fhappened upon their suspect.
OL,12,FManchester Crown Court heard three
OL,13,Fweeks after the grim discovery, two
OL,14,Fplain-clothes officers working on the
OL,15,Finquiry were driving an unmarked
OL,16,Fpolice car down a road in Salford,
OL,17,Fwhere they passed Majerkiewicz walking
OL,18,Fin the other direction.
