OL,6,FShortly afterwards, PC Paul Ashworth
OL,7,Fpulled his police car in front of the
OL,8,Fbus and boarded.
OL,10,FWatch the moment Majerkiewicz was
OL,11,Farrested and just some of the CCTV
OL,12,Fpolice used to track his movements:
OL,14,FBody-worn video footage played to the
OL,15,Fjury showed the officer telling the
OL,16,Fsuspect he was being detained to be
OL,17,Fsearched, before he was handcuffed and
OL,18,Ftaken off the bus.
