OL,6,FMajerkiewicz was told he had been
OL,7,Fidentified as a "person of interest"
OL,8,Fin a police investigation.
OL,10,FHe replied: "It's definitely a
OL,11,Fmistake, 100%."
OL,13,FPC Ashworth then tells Majerkiewicz he
OL,14,Fhas been seen on several occasions on
OL,15,FCCTV by police investigating a serious
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,FMajerkiewicz later says: "Someone
OL,19,Fsteal something?"
