OL,3,CHow thousands of hours of CCTV helped
OL,4,Cpolice catch a murderer
OL,6,FPC Ashworth replies: "It's a bit more
OL,7,Fserious than that, matey."
OL,9,FPolice found Majerkiewicz had on him
OL,10,Fthe phone and bank cards belonging to
OL,11,FMr Everett.
OL,13,FMinutes later, the officer then
OL,14,Fcautions Majerkiewicz, warning he is
OL,15,Fbeing arrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,17,F"What?" the suspect replies, before
OL,18,Fasking for a translator and shaking
OL,19,Fhis head.
