OL,3,CHow thousands of hours of CCTV helped
OL,4,Cpolice catch a murderer
OL,6,FDS Cullum says she her team were able
OL,7,Fto continue tracing a number of
OL,8,Fdifferent journeys made by
OL,9,FMajerkiewicz where he was visiting
OL,10,Fdeposition sites.
OL,12,F"The behaviour was different to what
OL,13,Fwe know, we normally go out with an
OL,14,Fempty bag, come back with our
OL,15,Fshopping," she said.
OL,17,F"He was leaving his home address with
OL,18,Fvery laden bags and coming back with
OL,19,Fno bags to hand."
