OL,3,CHow thousands of hours of CCTV helped
OL,4,Cpolice catch a murderer
OL,6,FFrom tracing his journeys, mostly
OL,7,Fusing buses, the team was able to
OL,8,Funveil a number of different sites
OL,9,Fincluding Boggart Hole Cluff, Worsley
OL,10,FWoods, Linneyshaw Colliery Wood, Black
OL,11,FBeach Reservoir, where more of Mr
OL,12,FEverett was discovered.
OL,14,F"It's anything but a coincidence
OL,15,Freally," she added. "When you, when
OL,16,Fyou put all the information together,
OL,17,Fthe CCTV, the phone data, the
OL,18,Fsearches, everything, it's like a
OL,19,Fjigsaw."
