OL,6,FDS Cullum describes how one of her
OL,7,Fteam members discovered remains of Mr
OL,8,FEverett as they were conducting their
OL,9,Finvestigations.
OL,11,FOn one occasion a member of GMP's VERA
OL,12,Fteam discovered Mr Everett's remains
OL,13,Fthemselves, after tracing a route
OL,14,Fbelieved to have been taken by
OL,15,FMajerkiewicz.
OL,17,F"It was very, very important for us
OL,18,Fall to find as much of Stuart as we
OL,19,Fcould," DS Cullum said.
